data.description: Situated on nearly 3 Acres of usable land, in the sprawling Lake Riverside Estates of Aguanga, sits an attractive open concept home. Through the front door you will enter into the Great Room with a Wall of Windows and Vaulted Ceilings. The Kitchen is up to date with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Two Master Bedrooms, one on each side of the house, lend to perfect privacy. Three additional bedrooms, all with new flooring. Large Laundry Room and a Walk In Pantry leave little to be desired. Spacious garage provides parking and additional storage area. Lot is located on a dead end road with very little drive by traffic. Living in Lake Riverside gives you access to numerous amenties....Such as the Private Airstrip, 55 acre Lake with Boat Dock and Launch, Community Center, Equestrain Arena, 55 miles of Groomed Roads, Picnic Area with BBQ, Playground and a Swimming Pool! Well maintained roads and a Private Security Patrol also make this a favorable place to live. New Propane tank placed, Well Test and new pressure tank/repairs, Septic Pump and Cert, And Termite Inspection ALL done in May 2023. Come Make it Yours!
